{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/extras/eww.png?t=1739361192\" /><strong><br>What Will Happen in the Demo?\u00a0</strong>\ud83d\udd75\ufe0f\u200d\u2642\ufe0f</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In The Enigma Case Demo, you will step into the shoes of a detective, searching for clues to solve a challenging case. The demo will take you to a caf\u00e9 scene where the investigation revolves around a specific event. Every detail matters! Carefully inspect the scene, gather clues, and uncover the mystery behind the crime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the demo, you'll encounter mini-games that will test your ability to find and analyze clues. Every correct move brings you closer to identifying the culprit, while mistakes may lead you astray. Can you demonstrate your detective skills and bring the criminal to justice?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now it's up to you to focus your attention and wits to solve the case! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you like our game, you can join our Discord channel and share your feedback. By the way, don't forget to add it to your wishlist! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/extras/UntitledProject-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1739361192\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various Cases</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Murders, accidents, suicides... Behind each case lies a completely different story waiting to be solved. You will need to use all your detective skills to succeed in these mysterious cases. But will you be able to unravel the mystery behind these cases?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/extras/ezgif-4-f18f02b116.gif?t=1739361192\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Detective Roles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Field Detective:</strong> You are the person with your finger on the pulse of the crime scene! It is your job to collect physical evidence, analyze clues and conduct one-on-one interviews with suspects.<strong>  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cyber Detective:</strong> It is your job to track the digital world! From social media accounts to emails, from GPS records to online traces, you will analyze every piece of digital evidence and find key information to solve the case. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/extras/ezgif-4-5b3477cd3b.gif?t=1739361192\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer Cooperation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Detective work doesn't have to be a one-man job! Team up with your friends and solve cases together.  It takes a team effort to uncover the truth!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In-Depth Reviews</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Security Cameras and Digital Evidence:</strong> Review security camera footage from the crime scene, collect and analyze digital evidence.   <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Add to Your Wish List</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please add our game to your wishlist and join our Discord to support us in development!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3271910?t=1739361192","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739361192","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271910/5c14de42ec3e0e57d035ddcfbe4ee2a7b711d8a3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739361192","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as